OL,3,CITV News given unprecedented access to
OL,4,Cprison Mother and Baby Unit
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Senior Political
OL,7,FProducer Lili Donlon-MansbridgeJFor
OL,8,Fnew mums 'Kelly' and Jada, getting a
OL,9,Fplace on the Mother and Baby Unit at
OL,10,FHMP New Hall was life-changing.
OL,12,FBoth women committed crimes which
OL,13,Flanded them with short custodial
OL,14,Fsentences. For both of them, it was
OL,15,Ftheir first offence.
OL,17,FThey feared the disruption being
OL,18,Flocked up would cause their families,
OL,19,Fand especially the impact it would
OL,20,Fhave on their babies, who weren't even
OL,21,Fa year old.
