OL,6,FBoth Kelly (not her real name) and
OL,7,FJada were given a place on the Mother
OL,8,Fand Baby Unit, a special and rare wing
OL,9,Fin some women prisons, where female
OL,10,Foffenders can serve their sentences
OL,11,Fwith their children.
OL,13,FSpaces are scarce; there are only
OL,14,Fseven units across the UK, and getting
OL,15,Fa place on then is hard, involving an
OL,16,Fapplication and multi-agency
OL,17,Feligibility assessment.
OL,19,FThey are also controversial.
