OL,6,FWorldwide, eleven countries have laws
OL,7,Fagainst sending pregnant women to
OL,8,Fprison. In the UK, pregnant women in
OL,9,Fprison are seven times more likely to
OL,10,Fsuffer a stillbirth. But for Kelly and
OL,11,FJada, the mother and baby unit
OL,12,Fprovided a lifeline.
