OL,6,FThe unit at HMP New Hall, was peaceful
OL,7,F- far quieter and softer than the
OL,8,Fother parts of the prison we visited.
OL,10,FThe unit sits separated from the main
OL,11,Festate, a smaller bungalow type
OL,12,Fbuilding leading onto an outside
OL,13,Fplaypark.
OL,15,FInside, there was cell space for ten
OL,16,Fmums and their babies, with a communal
OL,17,Flounge, playroom, multiple private
OL,18,Fbathrooms and an outdoor playpark. The
OL,19,Fspaces were filled with toys, nappies,
OL,20,Fprams, and books.
