OL,3,CITV News given unprecedented access to
OL,4,Cprison Mother and Baby Unit
OL,6,FOur cameras were granted this rare
OL,7,Faccess as the government prepares to
OL,8,Fradically overhaul the way women's
OL,9,Fjustice works in this country.
OL,11,FOne of the government's big focuses is
OL,12,Fon reforming the way pregnant women
OL,13,Fand mothers are sentenced.
OL,15,FThe issue is significant: one member
OL,16,Fof staff working at HMP New Hall told
OL,17,Fus around 80% of their current inmates
OL,18,Fhave children.
