OL,6,FKelly lives on the Mother and Baby
OL,7,FUnit with her newborn baby girl. We
OL,8,Fchatted on a bench outside, as she
OL,9,Frocked her baby in a buggy.
OL,11,FLots of the items, like buggies, toys
OL,12,Fand clothes the women use, are donated
OL,13,Fto the prison by local charities. The
OL,14,Funit has a nursery, run by Action for
OL,15,FChildren, which helps facilities play
OL,16,Factivities and visits for babies born
OL,17,For living in custody.
