OL,7,Fstreet robbery, which she says was
OL,8,Flinked to feeding her crack cocaine
OL,9,Fand heroin addiction. She was on the
OL,10,Frun from police when she found out she
OL,11,Fwas pregnant. That was when she
OL,12,Fdecided to hand herself in.
OL,14,F"I thought no way am I going to lose
OL,15,Fmy kid to social services," she told
OL,16,FITV New.
