OL,6,F"I thought I'd just stay at my mum's
OL,7,Fand the police came around and I just
OL,8,Fwent with them, cos I knew I were
OL,9,Fcoming back to prison, cos I thought
OL,10,Fwell it's a better chance for me to
OL,11,Fkeep my daughter than lose her."
OL,13,FShe told us that without the Mother
OL,14,Fand Baby Unit she has no doubt social
OL,15,Fservices would have removed her child
