OL,11,FThe government has broader ambitions
OL,12,Ffor reforming women in custody.
OL,14,FThe flagship government-commissioned
OL,15,FSentencing Review published last
OL,16,Fmonth, set out plans to reduce the
OL,17,Fnumber of women who are given short
OL,18,Fsentences, which currently make up 75%
OL,19,Fof female convictions.
