OL,6,FLegislation implementing some of these
OL,7,Frecommendations is due to be
OL,8,Fintroduced into Parliament imminently.
OL,10,FThe Sentencing Review argued that
OL,11,Fshort sentences aren't effective,
OL,12,Fparticularly when it comes to reducing
OL,13,Fre-offending.
OL,15,FIt also found there often isn't enough
OL,16,Ftime for prisons to provide any
OL,17,Frehabilitation, and work with inmates
OL,18,Fto address the reason they offended.
