OL,6,FThe report's author, Former
OL,7,FConservative Justice Secretary David
OL,8,FGauke, spoke exclusively to ITV News
OL,9,Fabout the changes last month.
OL,11,F"We think that too many people go
OL,12,Finside for a short period of time," he
OL,13,Fsaid. "They then come out unprepared
OL,14,Ffor reintegration into the community.
OL,15,FThat short sentence, if anything, has
OL,16,Fput them back."
