OL,6,FAlongside the work of the Sentencing
OL,7,FReview, the government this year
OL,8,Fcommissioned the first ever Women's
OL,9,FJustice Board, created specifically to
OL,10,Flook at ways to reduce the number of
OL,11,Fwomen in prison and increase the
OL,12,Fnumber supported in the community. One
OL,13,Fof its stated aims is to look for
OL,14,Fcommunity solutions, such as
OL,15,Fresidential alternatives to custody.
OL,17,FAbout three hours drive away from the
OL,18,Fprison is Willowdene Rehabilitation,
OL,19,Fone of those residential alternatives
OL,20,Fto custody. It is worlds away from HMP
OL,21,FNew Hall.
