OL,6,FWillowdene is nestled in the
OL,7,FShropshire countryside, based across a
OL,8,Ffarm. It is extremely rural: the
OL,9,Fnearest train station is nearly an
OL,10,Fhour's drive away. The site itself is
OL,11,Fso big you have to minibus around.
OL,12,FLast year, Willowdene supported over
OL,13,F400 women, on day schemes or on their
OL,14,Fresidential programme. It's funding is
OL,15,Fdone in yearly cycles, in part by
OL,16,Fgovernment, and in part through social
OL,17,Fenterprise.
