OL,6,FResidential offenders at Willowdene
OL,7,Fhave their own rooms, with private
OL,8,Fbathrooms. There are lounges and
OL,9,Fkitchens, and a private therapy room.
OL,11,FAnd significantly, women at Willowdene
OL,12,Fcan have much more access to their
OL,13,Fchildren.
OL,15,FThe staff help women initiate or
OL,16,Fmaintain contact with their children,
OL,17,Fand visits are more regular. For those
OL,18,Fthat whose children are being removed
OL,19,Fpermanently from their care,
